Net-SAP version 0.04
====================

Net::SAP currently provides basic functionality for receiving and parsing
SAP (RFC2974) multicast packets.




INSTALLATION

I now use Module::Build to build and install the module.
To install this module type the following:

   perl Build.PL
   ./Build
   ./Build test
   ./Build install

Module::Build is available in the debian package:

   libmodule-build-perl


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

	IO::Socket::Multicast
	Compress::Zlib

These are available in Debian as the packages:

	libio-socket-multicast-perl
	libcompress-zlib-perl


